Canada and USA, August 2008
===========================

1 to 3 August: San Francisco
----------------------------

Flying from Melbourne via Sydney.  (I `gain' a day.)

Meet/stay with relatives.

Meet Magdalen friends and Facebook friend.

Sunday: church at [Grace Cathedral](http://www.gracecathedral.org/), then lunch at the [Millennium Restaurant](http://www.millenniumrestaurant.com/).

4 to 8 August: Montréal
-----------------------

[World Student Christian Federation Senior Friends Gathering](http://www.scmcanada.org/ga2008/friends)

9 to 10 August: New York
------------------------

Taking the [Adirondack train](http://www.amtrak.com/servlet/ContentServer?pagename=Amtrak/am2Route/Vertical_Route_Page&c=am2Route&cid=1080842092695&ssid=134) from Montreal to New York City.

Meet Magdalen friends.

Home
----

Retrace my steps, or some other route?  (I `lose' a day.)
